Land of beautiful green terrains, lovely vast tea gardens, rich Tibetan culture and food and peaceful Buddhist monasteries. Yes, that’s Dharamshala for you. Nestled in the interriors of Himachal Pradesh, this Hill station offers best of all the worlds – the lovely scenic views of a hill station, the hustle bustle of a city in the busy Tibetan markets and localities with lovely small outdoor seating cafes where you could snuggle up and have a hot cuppa with steaming hot momos and is a perfect place to relax your mind while sitting in one of the Buddhist monasteries.